<p>Traveling this Holiday Season? Well if you're in Germany, you might be taking <a href="https://www.flixbus.de/">FlixBus</a>. And if you are, then chances are you just purchased your ticket on their new site hosted on Platform.sh. The site features a robust ticketing engine powered by the flexibility of <a href="https://drupalcommerce.org">Drupal Commerce</a> and was built by the talented team at <a href="http://www.wunderkraut.com/">Wunderkraut</a>, a Drupal Commerce Delivery partner that has just recently <a href="/about-us/news/commerce-guys-and-wunderkraut-announce-strategic-partnership-regarding-adoption">announced</a> their plans to move all the organizations development to <a href="https://platform.sh">Platform.sh</a>, our Continuous Delivery Cloud built to enable and enhance agile development from day one.</p>

